{"tid":1246690,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"膝患困擾要勁減40磅！67歲洪金寶近照曝光以輪椅代步","createTime":"2019-06-20T23:39:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T17:00:07.000Z","uid":41343,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7355de2308e2a38a83c4e735ff6004ddcf42d981","tid":1246690,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T23:39:59.000Z","msg":"年屆67歲的武打巨星洪金寶憑一身好功夫在影壇縱橫數十年，兩年前佢因舊患發作要接受膝蓋手術，開完刀後醫生提醒要少走動，仲叮囑佢減磅40磅減輕膝蓋負擔，而近日有網民影到洪金寶以電動輪椅代步。其實近年洪金寶為怕膝頭負荷過重平日多數以輪椅代步，有重要場合才用拐杖！<br />\n<br />\n近日有網友影到洪金寶坐著電動輪椅到街市買餸，見佢氣色相當好，精神奕奕咁揀海鮮，而另一張相他準備上車，而司機見有人拍照，立即用手遮掩鏡頭保護大哥。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/006uqhrogy1g46w9pfdzzj30i30o2dkg_16425545845d0b648110990.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2F006uqhrogy1g46w9pfdzzj30i30o2dkg_16425545845d0b648110990.jpg&h=b1d64e84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/006uqhrogy1g46wa63q15j30u0140tw2_11571681415d0b64828b44b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2F006uqhrogy1g46wa63q15j30u0140tw2_11571681415d0b64828b44b.jpg&h=d14f498a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fe8070b1e6875be2a03a8d7c6f2c5a554969fc2e","tid":1246690,"uid":75050,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T23:42:20.000Z","msg":"BOB <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nL9Y5JK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnL9Y5JK.jpg&h=0e2db74b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a19446064611ffc64dba09ea16f87ad526a0115e","tid":1246690,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T23:42:41.000Z","msg":"賞金獵人個心點諗"},{"pid":"a46e047b4d4fe9ef66f0c0310f6a608421fd26dc","tid":1246690,"uid":19725,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"c